Description:
Armor-piercing shells utilized by cannon weapons, such as the Mk6X series. Effective on light or medium-type warships.

Has increased effectiveness against penetrating or destroying hull armor, but lacks a high-explosive payload. Best used when followed-up by high-explosive shells.
